data.description: Here it is! Prime location in Branson!  Quaint Cape Cod Home on almost an acre. Downtown Branson near Lake Taneycomo, The Landing and the hospital.  This home boasts of lots of character. It was a custom built home with wall to wall brick fireplace, and cedar sided room upstairs. It's a 4 br, 2ba, 2 car garage, and 2 car carport and has plenty of room for parking several vehicles, boat, rv, whatever.  So convenient to  everything Branson has to offer-shows, shopping, restaurants and the lake.and the Landing. Home has new roof, new a/c, new hot water heater.. Make an appointment to see this one today. Only serious buyers need call.  Selling by Owner/Agent.
